title: How Come Consciousness?
itunes:subtitle: Philosophy Now Radio Show #36
itunes:author: Philosophy Now
description: Join Grant Bartley from Philosophy Now and guests Philip Goff from the University of Liverpool and Tom McClelland from the University of Manchester as they try to work out how all that electricity between your nerve cells relates to and produces all your experiences and thoughts. First broadcast on 25 May 2014 on Resonance FM.
